						 <p>Three bros go on a fun aquatic adventure! This super lighthearted and fun entry is surprisingly for Doomsday Contest! Check out Team Mikasa, and find out the source for the submarine at <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3534">SCP-3534</a>. Also check out War on All Fronts for the source for our whole contest!</p> <p>Enough plugging, thanks to these awesome peeps for critting and such (also tell me if I forgot anybody because I have a bad memory):<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/multizig" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3740504&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1527089749" alt="multizig" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3740504)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/multizig" >multizig</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lucavex-ayanami" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1348662&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1527089749" alt="Lucavex Ayanami" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1348662)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lucavex-ayanami" >Lucavex Ayanami</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dot-matrix" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4099802&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1527089749" alt="Dot Matrix" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4099802)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dot-matrix" >Dot Matrix</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-aers" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1856789&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1527089749" alt="Dr Aers" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1856789)" /></a><a href="http://www.wiki